room_title: Escape room "Obsidian Sword's Chamber of Horror" by Bamboozled Escape Room in Houston
review: Our family of 8, ranging in age from 8 to 72, all had a blast!!! Even though we did not escape, it was so much fun! I highly recommend and would do this again! So worth it!!

room_title: Escape room "Obsidian Sword's Chamber of Horror" by Bamboozled Escape Room in Houston
review: It was my first time to go to an escape room. Had a group of 10 of us for a birthday party. It was quite challenging but we worked together and managed to escape with over 10 minutes left! It was a lot of fun and want to go back and try some other rooms!
